client
dev tun
windows-driver wintun
proto tcp
remote 51.20.8.80 443
resolv-retry infinite
nobind
persist-key
persist-tun
remote-cert-tls server
cipher AES-256-CBC
verb 3

# ── SPLIT TUNNEL: only VPN subnet goes through tunnel ──
# Full tunnel would use: redirect-gateway def1
# We do NOT include redirect-gateway here.
# Only traffic to 10.8.0.0/24 goes through the VPN.
